{"tid":1631974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日風向：勇武退場","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T09:34:06.000Z","uid":228458,"like":64,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"ba19a739159f0b6b841a1924a5276d6f07cc5078","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:42.000Z","msg":"我之前都講過，唔係你唔岩聽就係帶風向。<br />\n其實我知有一部分人都係為左個運動好，先會打反思，又係大家話 「唔割」，不過每次行番動後要反思。而家問題係好多人做反思，你覺得唔岩聽就話人地帶風向，而做反思都唔等於分化、唔等於割蓆。<br />\n<br />\n以下係檢討：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: orange;\">國際線無可否認極為重要，逼到政府呢一步都主要因為國際線，所以國際反應係必需理會。</span><br />\n因此，如果真係裝修，必需要諗清楚間鋪係咪需要裝修，藍既係未至於要裝修，好怕大家遍地開花既時候，唔知有咩目標而亂揀目標。<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: orange;\">獅鳥裝修觀感上真係唔好睇 </span><br />\n唔好屌我住！唔割，我明白獅鳥裝修有佢既道理，但好多人唔明白點解要獅鳥裝修，好似優品360咁，有幾多人知係發生咩事？ 就係因為唔夠文宣！ <br />\n點解唔搞一日係文宣日，個個落哂連儂場貼文宣+向街坊解釋？沙田新城市就經常有呢個活動，好和諧，好理性咁做討論，去過就知我講咩，但我無見過其他區做。<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: orange;\"> 不用雷射筆射狗</span><br />\n我知有時手足撚狗撚得好開心，但雷射筆係傷唔到佢地，反而有藉口俾佢地清場。你可能會話，佢係咪都清架啦。係，但起碼都唔好俾藉口人先。另外，見過有手足射警署時射埋橋上既車，咁樣會影響到市民，仲可能有意外架。請注意。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">請不要被仇恨支配</span></span>，亦唔好變真暴徒，我地係香港人，有道德有智慧既香港人。<br />\n如果聽日真係遍地開花，請緊記以上既說話，唔好傷及無辜。"},{"pid":"44168f03d7b6c15b4d9c39a2b6677f1beb97c921","tid":1631974,"uid":177736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n不分化，不割蓆，不篤灰</span>"},{"pid":"a81ec8852a4707bc99665b5b1022bdca00e657ae","tid":1631974,"uid":130079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:41.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"0921fef67fe9536e59945c22b11e951468ee62b7","tid":1631974,"uid":133728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jYtuLaR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjYtuLaR.jpg&h=f5ef1ebb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89e2dcc3239b5196a40ed4e37fd5b2836398bcd1","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a8bf62871ba1bfc0a712f1ec1189aa94302481d5","tid":1631974,"uid":89923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:52.000Z","msg":"其實只係提出太多裝修唔好 唔代表割蓆<br />\n<br />\n話明核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"3cd0c8101caa966f354b26e5f4d05706c6193b9d","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:11.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"eb893efc35d828ed973a1fcc7ab683df4d3bfe83","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"aa55c4ec57b0c6a26e79d10ffd6247e549ae68cd","tid":1631974,"uid":272030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:50.000Z","msg":"建議美國法案通過前 而勇武又想法案前放慢步調 可以搞記者會 宣布暫時停止升級行動 (某些裝修可以暫援 黨鐵必須繼續）但說明不是因為禁蒙面法 （理論上政府呢步棋 勇武定和理都被政府佔主導 想不被主導 必須有明確聲明）而是等待高官們接受美國的制裁 同時設立死線（法案後） 若繼續違返民意（其實之前可以搞公投）法案後跟美國一齊制裁特區政府（do everything you like) <br />\nwe connect with USA<br />\n<br />\n若勇武不想 尊重你們的想法 <br />\n不割蓆"},{"pid":"af59fd9487623f998256cc6b6e2d91327c296d38","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:53.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0248ab1d97c047ed112e4a43c6b9fd23a898fd7e","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:08.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b1b3c08f3aa56dd95c689f42d0a620caa9c7542c","tid":1631974,"uid":153186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:11.000Z","msg":"先降半級 黑色只限港共建築物+黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f247717d43a40684e9898f1d62c8a24b795630db","tid":1631974,"uid":116074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:14.000Z","msg":"推(1/10)"},{"pid":"60d9b051df3f3c8fdebe3459c52071e8b5118990","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:45.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"04c22f849827f87cf6dc857f3f3feb12be5e5882","tid":1631974,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:48.000Z","msg":"新金寶茶餐廳 - 石硤尾南昌街113號地下"},{"pid":"5b6d54479fe07bf18d1803ccd4330201ae543984","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"40e12bcd4f22e47f47764bff81170c563980bce3","tid":1631974,"uid":199622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:18.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"164e5e0414ca71e3c8f4b2f2bf0b2b620c91288b","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:27.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e7686ab263f07eb1e3cebd3b7d66436e89b26472","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"540c270538fbdec680f28731aecc27e8d7fbb8d9","tid":1631974,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:12.000Z","msg":"蒙面法前後戴口罩嘅意義唔同咗 而依個意義應該決定我地嘅行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630541</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bd4eed48c8f475a63f713bfd85fcd6e349979429","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:21.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"46e2e82e63c022757069a7afecc3579f6afcfc2a","tid":1631974,"uid":232197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:49:17.000Z","msg":"樓主講得幾好,希望各位都退後一步諗,每步棋每個決定都係好關鍵"},{"pid":"7077c981d90318d42b7fdae06779fa7c06e1ce50","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:49:28.000Z","msg":"另一樣野 裝修唔好用火魔法 會殃及池魚"},{"pid":"ecc2f5b1fe70a852b58e69a795f0e0627280746a","tid":1631974,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:50:00.000Z","msg":"宜家雷射筆比我攞嚟搵返我Team人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n射狗完全冇撚用"},{"pid":"6e10186070a0dc4956378db19ded117d9ed86c1e","tid":1631974,"uid":219117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:50:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fb37ee2976e9b67d36510fd12c138c261f21836","tid":1631974,"uid":156679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:50:27.000Z","msg":"反思求進化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1643c073de7a61f35875f8f6537acc86bf1df2","tid":1631974,"uid":320881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:51:24.000Z","msg":"P牌求幫推<br />\n<br />\n[正視聽] 每個動作嘅&quot;用途&quot;及&quot;代價&quot;<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631863</a>"},{"pid":"ed40829e27c8af74c36382b03ce169caade021da","tid":1631974,"uid":57566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:00.000Z","msg":"對於第三個point<br />\n當班狗用強光照手足或記者既時候<br />\n我地還擊好合理"},{"pid":"06bfa8b056e72e1cf85b1f3eecd35fb6c4feac1e","tid":1631974,"uid":15259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"87996daba2ebb4d736512192ae8d8a502189e4d2","tid":1631974,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:16.000Z","msg":"[遍地落區公投] 連登已被嚴重滲透，任何風向公投都唔應該再係連登搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631914</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"25573b9493cae5eda9bc744e042d601b5b71b458","tid":1631974,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44168f03d7b6c15b4d9c39a2b6677f1beb97c921","tid":1631974,"uid":177736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n不分化，不割蓆，不篤灰</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[18區開花] 一句講晒，聽日一點定八點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631933</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"609622c87856bb462f24330fec6f457bd8d91511","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46e2e82e63c022757069a7afecc3579f6afcfc2a","tid":1631974,"uid":232197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"reply