6e2e82e63c022757069a7afecc3579f6afcfc2a","tid":1631974,"uid":232197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:49:17.000Z","msg":"樓主講得幾好,希望各位都退後一步諗,每步棋每個決定都係好關鍵"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:36.000Z","msg":"有時見到真係好灰心，幫手打檢討俾人話五毛<br />\n想講，前線都有做錯既時候，都要檢討，唔係唔岩聽就風向同分化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:31.000Z","msg":"勇武手足真係要冷靜下,唔好係唔係都裝修.<br />\n另外唔割還唔割,但係要識<span style=\"color: red;\">檢討</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">反思</span>行動到底好唔好.<br />\n另外要識控制自己情緒.<br />\n有唔少PO都有反映影相GE問題.自己<span style=\"color: red;\">做好BLACK BLOC</span>就唔怕被人影.<br />\n如果真係擔心影到其他手足,請有<span style=\"color: red;\">禮貌</span>請佢出示手機GE相片內容.<br />\n點解今日香港市民會對班狗群起圍之,原因在於佢地GE行為完全唔合比例呀MA.<br />\n如果手足淪落到好似班狗咁,唔好怪其他中立或者淺黃轉向對家.<br />\n因為手足GE行為同狗無異.<br />\n切記呀手足!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066d36d1abd4d6daffcb5fdf67b1f3e6e6eac6e3","tid":1631974,"uid":120431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1b3c08f3aa56dd95c689f42d0a620caa9c7542c","tid":1631974,"uid":153186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:11.000Z","msg":"先降半級 黑色只限港共建築物+黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54614420a18ec34b6636b56e26c868bdb6efde62","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"真係想多謝勇武既 真係要有好大勇氣先做到 <br />\n不過個個都可以做勇武 有時真係仇恨曚閉左眼睛<br />\n所以希望大家諗清楚先行動"},{"pid":"3eea9f702db1e75b78a99b249c27f0624629f95b","tid":1631974,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:44.000Z","msg":"中共<span style=\"color: red;\">無理</span>出老解, <span style=\"color: red;\">8964</span>, 之後被國際制裁<br />\n中共<span style=\"color: red;\">合理</span>出老解, <span style=\"color: red;\">新彊</span>, 然後就沒有了然後<br />\n<br />\n手足要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95606c07edc8e9475563cd2bc5729fe168cc6647","tid":1631974,"uid":89923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:11.000Z","msg":"可以集中黨鐵先, 兩次之後佢一定重兵守, 我地再轉陣"},{"pid":"c4a14ea287c392d70811a672a265c1536e1a22b6","tid":1631974,"uid":23094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n唔代表 不檢討 不反省<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n雷射筆射狗真係冇乜用<br />\n要用就用得實用啲<br />\n例如指遠處位置畀身邊手足睇<br />\n唔係用嚟射Popo，又傷唔到佢，仲暴露自己位置<br />\n同埋唔好低估Popo啲鏡頭"},{"pid":"324b020f0ed29df77462798ceaf1282fce134119","tid":1631974,"uid":76813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:24.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"022894c525e7bbe69b991a52caf33c0a3ff70708","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:07:52.000Z","msg":"仲有，就算勇武停幾日都唔叫失敗<br />\n革命之火係心既 以前都只係 weekend先出 <br />\n而家幾乎日日出 勇武都攰啦！ <br />\n唔係話唔出 只係隔耐少少 比文宣都做埋野"},{"pid":"9cfbe04aaf9896b86c3463178e2037cea5cc5d9f","tid":1631974,"uid":242867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:15:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"45e7bad4f8a22f40073fe5c35e8359bb3e8632fc","tid":1631974,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:16:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c14cff2e0ab8a5d31a8ff75620d5db19e8dec84","tid":1631974,"uid":232197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609622c87856bb462f24330fec6f457bd8d91511","tid":1631974,"uid":228458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46e2e82e63c022757069a7afecc3579f6afcfc2a","tid":1631974,"uid":232197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:49:17.000Z","msg":"樓主講得幾好,希望各位都退後一步諗,每步棋每個決定都係好關鍵"},"citedBy":2,"repl